Text.SourceString: It's raining. Plants happy to get water.
Text.LocalizedString: It's raining. Plants happy to get water.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Giu</> like rain sound. It's calming. Goom...
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Giu</> like rain sound. It's calming. Goom...

Text.SourceString: When it rains, everything fresh and new.
Text.LocalizedString: When it rains, everything fresh and new.

Text.SourceString: Storms powerful. Best to stay safe inside.
Text.LocalizedString: Storms powerful. Best to stay safe inside.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Giu</> watch lightning and listen to thunder. It's exciting, little scary.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Giu</> watch lightning and listen to thunder. It's exciting, little scary.

Text.SourceString: After big storm, world looks different.
Text.LocalizedString: After big storm, world looks different.

Text.SourceString: Snow falling beautiful. Goom goom...
Text.LocalizedString: Snow falling beautiful. Goom goom...

Text.SourceString: Everything quiet when it snows. It's peaceful.
Text.LocalizedString: Everything quiet when it snows. It's peaceful.

Text.SourceString: Snow fun but cold.
Text.LocalizedString: Snow fun but cold.

Text.SourceString: Snow season here. Everything slow down. Time for rest.
Text.LocalizedString: Snow season here. Everything slow down. Time for rest.

Text.SourceString: Sprouting season here. Everything starts grow again.//Time to eat.
Text.LocalizedString: Sprouting season here. Everything starts grow again.//Time to eat.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Giu</> like sprouting season.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Giu</> like sprouting season.

Text.SourceString: This season busy for planting.//Giants eat.
Text.LocalizedString: This season busy for planting.//Giants eat.

Text.SourceString: Gardening peaceful. <NpcName>Giu</> enjoy quiet and seeing results.
Text.LocalizedString: Gardening peaceful. <NpcName>Giu</> enjoy quiet and seeing results.

Text.SourceString: Watering plants favorite part. Goom goom!
Text.LocalizedString: Watering plants favorite part. Goom goom!

Text.SourceString: Forest animals interesting. All have different ways.
Text.LocalizedString: Forest animals interesting. All have different ways.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Giu</> like listening to birds.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Giu</> like listening to birds.

Text.SourceString: Watching squirrels fun. They always busy.
Text.LocalizedString: Watching squirrels fun. They always busy.

Text.SourceString: Forest full of life. Every animal has place. Goom...
Text.LocalizedString: Forest full of life. Every animal has place. Goom...

Text.LocalizedString: Cooking fun. <NpcName>Giu</> like human food.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Giu</> respect <NpcName>Gort</>. Trying to make things right not easy.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Giu</> respect <NpcName>Gort</>. Trying to make things right not easy.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Giu</> love <NpcName>Gort</>.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Giu</> love <NpcName>Gort</>.

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Gort</> powerful, learned to be careful with power.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Gort</> powerful, learned to be careful with power.

Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Gort</>and <NpcName>Giu</> not always agree, but <NpcName>Giu</> always love him.

Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Giu</> not know how to make human food. You teach, question?

Text.SourceString: You make human food, give to Giants. We like.
Text.LocalizedString: You make human food, give to Giants. We like.

Text.SourceString: Magic not scare you. <NpcName>Giu</> see humans. Easily scared.//You special.
Text.LocalizedString: Magic not scare you. <NpcName>Giu</> see humans. Easily scared.//You special.

Text.SourceString: You live on large land. Why so big, question?
Text.LocalizedString: You live on large land. Why so big, question?

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Giu</> hear you gardening. You're loud.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Giu</> hear you gardening. You're loud.

Text.SourceString: Cows large. If <NpcName>Giu</> eat lot of grass, maybe <NpcName>Giu</> get large like cows.//<NpcName>Giu</> need try that.
Text.LocalizedString: Cows large. If <NpcName>Giu</> eat lot of grass, maybe <NpcName>Giu</> get large like cows.//<NpcName>Giu</> need try that.

Text.SourceString: You have cows, question? Can <NpcName>Giu</> come play with cows, question?
Text.LocalizedString: You have cows, question? Can <NpcName>Giu</> come play with cows, question?

Text.SourceString: <NpcName>Giu</> learning speak to cows. Hard language, harder than human.
Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Giu</> learning speak to cows. Hard language, harder than human.

Text.SourceString: Cows have big ears. Must be nice have big ears.
Text.LocalizedString: Cows have big ears. Must be nice have big ears.

Text.LocalizedString: Chieftain say born way we are. <NpcName>Giu</> not be cow, cow not be <NpcName>Giu</>.

Text.LocalizedString: You have fancy clothes. Where get, question?

Text.LocalizedString: <NpcName>Giu</> went to your land this morning. Got lost.

Text.LocalizedString: You tall. <NpcName>Giu</> not tall.

Text.LocalizedString: Chieftain say no cows in village. No space for them.

Text.LocalizedString: You need lot of water to cool off. You tall.

Text.LocalizedString: We miss <NPCName>Gort</>, twin. You find <NPCName>Gort</> too?
